Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.51,0:00:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,. I want to understand\Nhow you move our money. Well, I can be on site\Nwithin 12 hours
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.25,0:00:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to begin withdrawing funds\Nfrom your Caracas accounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.26,0:00:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I convert to bonds\Nas an air gap safeguard
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.13,0:00:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,so that\Nthe liquid capital
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.67,0:00:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,cannot be electronically\Ntracked.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.40,0:00:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I then reconvert for deposit,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.54,0:00:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and the funds are\Ncontrolled here digitally.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.51,0:00:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You can access your accounts\Nfrom anywhere in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.35,0:00:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What guarantees\Ndo we have?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.23,0:00:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Of safety, of security?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Your reputation\Nprecedes you, but --
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.23,0:00:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We are not men you fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.77,0:00:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Gentlemen, nobody can rob a bank\Nthat's always on the move.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Our portfolios.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.57,0:00:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You protect them\Nwith your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.74,0:00:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.64,0:00:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.55,0:01:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall begin setting up\Nyour accounts immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.59,0:01:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, an attendant\Nwill be in with some beverages.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.22,0:01:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Mierce's worked wonders\Nfor you, Weecha.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.49,0:01:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Your recovery so far\Nis absolutely remarkable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.50,0:02:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What you both have\Naccomplished is a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.21,0:02:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's time for me\Nto get back to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.35,0:02:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Weecha, you were nearly dead\Na week ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.32,0:02:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You need\Nto continue to rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.42,0:02:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Eat good food, take naps,\Nread a book, listen to music.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.23,0:02:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I belong\Nout there with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.64,0:02:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You belong here getting\Nstronger with your sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,if she'll stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.26,0:02:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting\Nthe cold shoulder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.39,0:02:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She told me she still thinks\Nthis place is no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.57,0:02:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,For whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.80,0:02:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Any of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She needs time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.81,0:02:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She said a fire ceremony may\Nhelp guide her path.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:39.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A fire ceremony\Nin an Airstream?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly what does\None of those entail?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:43.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you do it outside\Non the grill?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.43,0:02:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Raymond, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.70,0:02:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she needs to consult\Nthe other side for guidance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.91,0:02:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Who on the other side,\Nand what other side?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Mierce,\Nwe're right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.82,0:02:55.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.29,0:02:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Marvin.\NHello.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this must be\Nthe famous Mierce.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.93,0:03:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello. I'm Marvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.57,0:03:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Raymond has told me\Nso much about you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and how glad\Nhe is that you're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.28,0:03:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Raymond\Nsays a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.50,0:03:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, did I come\Nat a bad time?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.47,0:03:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I've experienced\Nhostage situations
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.51,0:03:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,that are less tense\Nthan this trailer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.72,0:03:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep visiting,\Nand the trailer
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.59,0:03:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,seems to keep getting smaller\Nand smaller and smaller, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.96,0:03:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know,\NI guess time will tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.33,0:03:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep your fingers, legs,\Nand eyes crossed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.70,0:03:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But I sent you on a chase.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.67,0:03:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope it wasn't of\Nthe "wild goose" variety.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.78,0:03:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a statement of\Nthe bank account in question.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.45,0:03:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The same one used to pay\Nfor the murders
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of the Lacroixs\Nand Reggie Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.53,0:03:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You were right --\Nit's a numbered account
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.66,0:03:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,held at Caelum Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.80,0:03:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Heaven's vault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.94,0:03:55.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Marvin, I haven't done\Nany banking
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.54,0:03:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,with Harris Gramercy\Nin, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.28,0:03:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Years.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.61,0:04:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And no new accounts have\Nbeen opened in your absence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.48,0:04:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You still hold several accounts\Non that plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.56,0:04:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Those accounts\Nare still active?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:07.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we never\Nclosed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No place is safer than Caelum\Nfor those funds.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.00,0:04:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Fair point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.54,0:04:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Raymond, someone had access\Nto this account
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.51,0:04:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and paid for those murders,\Nand they may also be responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.01,0:04:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,for the death\Nof Kate's sister, Maureen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.75,0:04:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Problem is\Nit's a joint account.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Electronic petty cash,\Naccessible worldwide
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.86,0:04:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,for operational expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.37,0:04:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know how many\Nof our people had access?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.77,0:04:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do we start?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.78,0:04:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We start on the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The scary call\Nis very much
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.02,0:04:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,coming from\Ninside the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So you reached out to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.90,0:04:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we've had experience\Ntogether with Caelum Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.54,0:04:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you take on Gramercy,\Nyou better be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.55,0:04:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone paid for the deaths\Nof Reggie Cole,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.62,0:04:54.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tyson Lacroix,\NMichelle Lacroix,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,and used a Reddington\Naccount to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.83,0:04:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This same someone\Nblackmailed Harold Cooper
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and is almost\Ncertainly responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,for Elizabeth's death
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.54,0:05:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,and probably the same\Nfor Maureen Rowan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Look into my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.05,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe\Nevery word of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That's your assurance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.53,0:05:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a bank on a plane,\Nactually several planes
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.47,0:05:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,with one main branch\Nwith a man named Harris Gramercy
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.44,0:05:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,as the chairman, president,\Nand head teller.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.45,0:05:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It operates like\Na ghost plane --
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.89,0:05:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,no flight plans filed\Nand no GPS transponder.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,On top of which, its onboard\Nsevers are protected
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.54,0:05:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,from outside interference
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.07,0:05:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,with elliptic curve\Ncryptography.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No one is hacking their way\Ninside there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never been this close\Nto an answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm inches away,\Nand I can't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.43,0:05:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I need Harris Gramercy to tell\Nme who accessed that account.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.00,0:05:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And you and I both know\Nhe's the only person who can.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:56.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Caelum works under\Nstrict secrecy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:05:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Both the accounts and clients\Nare identified by numbers,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,and only verified clients\Nmay access the accounts.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Val Messick was the assassin\Npaid to kill
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.63,0:06:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,the Lacroixs and Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.90,0:06:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He was paid with\NReddington's account 4626329.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So we just need the number\Nof the client who accessed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not\Ngonna be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.71,0:06:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to match\Na number to a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.98,0:06:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't force Gramercy\Nto give you information.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.49,0:06:18.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said anything\Nabout forcing?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,By the time I'm finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.49,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll be happy to\Ngive me what I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.50,0:06:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're gonna run a con\Non the president Caelum Bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't very well put a gun\Nto his head,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,not with\Nthe friends he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we get him\Non the ground,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure\NHarris will be reasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:34.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If we help you with this,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.89,0:06:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,once this is over,\Nthe FBI keeps him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever you want.\NWhat do I care?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're losing focus.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.03,0:06:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gramercy\Nisn't the goal here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.60,0:06:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,finding Elizabeth's\Nkiller is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.14,0:06:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My focus is clear\Non Harold Cooper's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.78,0:06:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If the information on that plane\Nhelped to vindicate
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that man, that's my goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So how do we ground him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.16,0:06:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Raymond has a plan, but the FAA\Nisn't going to like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, um, can we talk?\NI have news.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.11,0:07:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course,\Nbut we're gonna need
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.55,0:07:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,to get on it\Nto find this plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.95,0:07:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, I'm sorry,\Nbut I heard from Main Justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,They processed your review,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're revoking\Nyour field status
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.76,0:07:12.10,Default,,0,0,0,,due to medical liabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let you work this case,\Nat least --
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.17,0:07:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,at least not in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.78,0:07:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I was talking\Nwith a friend
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.08,0:07:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,recently about the first time\NI ever flew on this plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.82,0:07:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was a turbulent\Nride then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.70,0:07:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course that's also\Na turbulent friendship now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess no matter\Nwhere you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.97,0:07:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you should prepare\Nfor rough air.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.08,0:07:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Raymond,\Nyou have a lot of money
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.98,0:07:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,in this bank,\Nwhich is why I was obligated
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.22,0:07:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,to take this meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.79,0:07:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So what\Ncan I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.70,0:07:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a favor, Harris.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.58,0:07:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's this?\NA cricket score?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.65,0:07:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You have every account\Non this plane
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,locked up in that safe deposit\Nbox mind of yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That one belongs to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I need the name\Nof the last person
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.02,0:08:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,who made a withdrawal\Nfrom that account.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.19,0:08:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your account.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.73,0:08:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You should already know\Nwho's accessing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.99,0:08:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It is my account, so you\Nshould have no problem
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,telling me who made\Nthe withdrawal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.64,0:08:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you know the rules.\NNo names.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.04,0:08:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If my clients found out --\NI'm a client.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:29.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.15,0:08:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would\Nanyone else care?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were to give out one name,\Nthe perception would be
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.76,0:08:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,that I'm likely to\Ngive out others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.03,0:08:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If someone is accessing\Nyour money,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,it's because they had\Npermission from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.04,0:08:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you don't know\Nwho that is, well,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.24,0:08:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid there's nothing else\NI can tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,How's the tracker holding up?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got him pinpointed\Nwithin a geographic meter.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.00,0:08:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.70,0:08:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Under Title II of
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.13,0:08:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the Intelligence Reform\Nand Terrorism
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.64,0:08:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Prevention Act of 2004,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:58.18,Default,,0,0,0,,the FBI has authority\Nto investigate any threats
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.18,0:08:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to national security\Npursuant --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.91,0:09:01.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What language\Nare you speaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,As acting director\Nof an FBI task force,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.05,0:09:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a credible threat\Nof terrorist action
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,to US Route 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.13,0:09:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,The Overseas Highway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ground all flight traffic.\NNow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.80,0:09:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got six flights\Nleaving Key West,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.71,0:09:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a billionaire\Nlanding at Key Largo,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've got a soccer team
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:16.88,Default,,0,0,0,,sitting on the runway\Nin Marathon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.88,0:09:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me to --\NGround them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.08,0:09:19.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Or my next call will be\Nto the Air Force
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.82,0:09:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to ground them for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.32,0:09:24.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We can start with a plane that\Nis not on your ground radar.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.30,0:09:26.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I have its coordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.70,0:09:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, excuse me, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We were just informed\Nthat we are currently over
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:34.65,Default,,0,0,0,,United States airspace and\Nmust land under its authority.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.65,0:09:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Have they told you why?\NNo, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But we were encouraged\Nto comply under threat
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.62,0:09:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of the US Air Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:42.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then, by all means,\Ncomply.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Copy that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps we\Nshould drink up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.84,0:09:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.75,0:09:52.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing that a little\Ntalk or time
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.12,0:09:54.89,Default,,0,0,0,,or perhaps a small donation\Ncan't fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not entirely\Ncomfortable with
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.06,0:10:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,an unscheduled\Nstop like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It was better\Nthan an F-16
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.71,0:10:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,blasting the two of us\Nout of the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This feels unsafe, Harris.\NPlease fix it promptly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.11,0:10:11.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need a moment to speak\Nto whomever is in charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.36,0:10:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,FBI!\NWe have a credible threat,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.73,0:10:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and we've had to ground\Nall air traffic now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.00,0:10:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you gentlemen would\Ngive us a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll inspect your plane\Nand have you on your way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy to\Nassist a US agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I know your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know who you are!\NYou're Raymond Reddington.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's he talking about?\NMe? I don't know that man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.40,0:10:34.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Redmond Rillington?\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.87,0:10:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-Let's go.\N0-All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.11,0:10:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone on this plane\Nis under arrest.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.88,0:10:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell\Nis happening here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,. Hello, Val.\NHow you been? You're the fed\Nwho arrested me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:57.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.35,0:11:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You've come to personally\Nescort me to detention?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,See this?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.12,0:11:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not escorting\Nyou anywhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.43,0:11:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're not\Ngoing to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.03,0:11:06.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a transfer order.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.27,0:11:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to\Nwitness protection
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.70,0:11:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,because you snitched\Non the people who hired you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.11,0:11:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.08,0:11:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,This says you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.45,0:11:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,And we had you\Non triple homicide,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.02,0:11:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,so you must've really\Ngiven up the goods.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.02,0:11:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.19,0:11:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You get\Nhanded over to WitSec,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.93,0:11:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,they begin your paperwork\Nfor induction.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That process is long enough\Nthat anyone paying attention --
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:32.05,Default,,0,0,0,,like the person who hired you --\Ncan get word that you snitched.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.05,0:11:33.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Then WitSec follows up with me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and I suddenly have no record of\Nyou helping on an active case.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when you're cooling your\Nheels in central detention.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.44,0:11:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You, a known snitch, sitting\Nin gen pop the length of time
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.74,0:11:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it takes for me\Nto make up my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.98,0:11:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's\Na death sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a man with\Na lot to lose, Val.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.35,0:11:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,So I really don't care\Nabout you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.06,0:11:55.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I could misplace\Nthis piece of paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and then you go to trial\Nlike you're supposed to,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:11:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and no one is the wiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.51,0:12:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Triple homicide?\NYou'll be a big man on campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You might even make some friends\Nto keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.95,0:12:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you\Nwant to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.32,0:12:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Who hired you and everything\Nyou were paid to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Spare no detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.40,0:12:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I never got a name, and you know\Nwhat I was paid to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.07,0:12:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This van is leaving\Nin five minutes, Val.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.98,0:12:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you want it\Nto take you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.09,0:12:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There was one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.09,0:12:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,After I killed\NMichelle Lacroix,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.40,0:12:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I was supposed to go\Nto the Lacroix house,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but you\Narrested me first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.27,0:12:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And do what at the house?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.11,0:12:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Burn it to the ground\Nand start the fire near
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.88,0:12:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Lacroix's desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.26,0:12:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've had nightmares\Nthat begin this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.06,0:12:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm in federal custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.13,0:12:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My plane impounded full of the\Nmost sensitive banking data
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.88,0:12:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.38,0:12:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Raymond, what the hell\Nare we gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.05,0:12:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Federal or not,\Nthey're all just cops.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I can\Nget us out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.43,0:13:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.40,0:13:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,We haven't been given\Nour phone call yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.61,0:13:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A while ago, I won a game\Nof roque
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.14,0:13:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,against the lieutenant governor\Nof Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.28,0:13:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He owes me a huge favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,One call gets the both of us\Nout of here -- or just me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.16,0:13:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not giving up a client\Nto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If the FBI starts\Npoking around that plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.47,0:13:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll be giving up\Na lot more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:26.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a real villain,\Naren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.31,0:13:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This villain can have\Nyou airborne within the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,One name seems a small price\Nto pay for your freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.16,0:13:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.60,0:13:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This situation, as sudden\Nand horrible as it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.17,0:13:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,seems to have greatly\Nimproved your ability
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,to make requests,\Nhasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.58,0:13:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying\Nto say, Harris?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.18,0:13:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Under no circumstances\Nknown to God or man
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.02,0:13:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,will I cooperate with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.32,0:13:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, now you're just\Nbeing unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.46,0:13:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't expose any of\Nyour other clients
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.60,0:13:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,to tell me about a transfer\Nfrom my own account.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.94,0:14:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it exposes me,\Nbecause I represent something --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.52,0:14:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Trust in me.\NTrust in my bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.19,0:14:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,People come to me not just\Nto protect their money,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.36,0:14:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but to protect\Ntheir secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.93,0:14:12.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I do not\Ndivulge names.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.64,0:14:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I am a man of my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.21,0:14:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'm a man of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.38,0:14:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You should\Nreconsider, Harris.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.22,0:14:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that a threat?\NI'm Redmond Rillington.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.59,0:14:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to make threats,\NI just have to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.46,0:14:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This entire arrest is a sham.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.13,0:14:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, were those even\Nreal agents earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.64,0:14:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got nothing to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.61,0:14:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Just the man in this cell\Nwith you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:37.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a nice speech\Nyou gave --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.52,0:14:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,all that trust\Nand trusting --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.00,0:14:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,but you're certainly\Nno paragon of virtue, Harris.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.00,0:14:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I know where the money\Nin your bank comes from --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.24,0:14:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,criminals, war lords,\Ndrug dealers,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.55,0:14:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,bankers, and politicians\Nwho've defrauded nations.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.95,0:14:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we find out\Nif this 9mm is a sham?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.53,0:14:59.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.36,0:15:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.44,0:15:05.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Gee, I guess it's\Na real gun after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.24,0:15:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to get in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.48,0:15:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,That man may have the name\Nof the person
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.02,0:15:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,who ordered\NLiz's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.25,0:15:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So we do nothing?\NGive it a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.42,0:15:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not losing sleep\Nover some criminal banker.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.06,0:15:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, where are the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.57,0:15:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone must've\Nheard that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.04,0:15:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But you called it, Harris.\NThere are no police.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.27,0:15:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't even\Nan active station.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.01,0:15:24.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why they brought us\Nin the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.28,0:15:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just you and me.\NI need an ambulance.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.62,0:15:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.23,0:15:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep a backup log\Nof all transactions
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.47,0:15:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,with a colleague in Riga,\Njust numbers on paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.11,0:15:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, God.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.58,0:15:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't want it\Nto play out like this,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,but now that is has,\Njust get me the name.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.70,0:15:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Ego confido in pecunia 123.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.58,0:15:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I need\Nthe transfer history
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:16:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,of account number 4626329.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.32,0:16:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Just -- just give me\Nthe last line details.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Client 4836924, got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.07,0:16:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, 4836924.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.65,0:16:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You know who it is,\Ntell me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.06,0:16:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.73,0:16:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hedwig Hawkins.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.36,0:16:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Heddie?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.70,0:16:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Numbers don't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.47,0:16:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, I -- I need\Nan ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.05,0:16:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.77,0:16:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You followed me down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.47,0:17:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,You are absolutely\Nincorrigible, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.31,0:17:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Your sister allowed this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.81,0:17:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She didn't know I left.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She was out shopping\Nfor her ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.78,0:17:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my God, we are\Ngoing to pay and pay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.76,0:17:10.67,Default,,0,0,0,,At least give her a call,\Nlet her know you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.66,0:17:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you you're\Nnot well enough yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.13,0:17:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,If something happens --
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You needed\Na ride so sit back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.81,0:17:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.39,0:17:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is\NFederal Agent Zuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I need an ambulance\Nfor a gunshot wound
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.17,0:17:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,at gulf and aviation\Nright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.71,0:17:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This blood's dark. I think\Nthe bullet hit his liver.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.88,0:17:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.35,0:17:39.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, we got the name,\Ndidn't we?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:42.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We did.\NGod help Heddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,. This is all from\NLacroix's home office? I had an evidence team\Nbag every shelf and cabinet
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.85,0:17:55.45,Default,,0,0,0,,near his desk.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.45,0:17:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's where Val Messick was told\Nto start the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.49,0:17:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It stands to reason\Nsomeone wanted
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.19,0:18:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to make sure it burned\Nmore than anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.83,0:18:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll start at this end,\Nyou start at that end.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You know why I'm here\Nhelping you
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.88,0:18:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and not down in Florida\Nwith the rest of the team?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured you'd tell me\Nwhen you were comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.53,0:18:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been demoted\Nto a desk role.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.20,0:18:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The headaches?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.30,0:18:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't blame Aram.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.17,0:18:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He only did what I asked.\NI was honest in my own review.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.68,0:18:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He did his job\Nby submitting it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.48,0:18:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm frustrated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.49,0:18:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Believe me, I know\Na thing or two
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.53,0:18:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,about feeling\Nfrustrated lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.50,0:18:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We just keep working.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,How was Gramercy\Nwhen you left?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Headed into surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.52,0:18:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd lost a lot of blood.\NIt was 50/50.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.92,0:18:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It gets worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.42,0:18:50.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He realized it was a ruse\Nbefore Raymond shot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.23,0:18:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't think\Nwe were real FBI.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means, if he survives,\Nwe have to let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.90,0:18:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only way to\Nprotect Mr. Reddington.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.70,0:18:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,We need\Nto protect Heddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.81,0:19:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it conceivable she could be\Nbehind any of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,All we have is an account\Nthat led to her name.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.59,0:19:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know enough yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.92,0:19:05.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Reddington will kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.52,0:19:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already left\None person for dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.89,0:19:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to\Nkeep Heddie alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.80,0:19:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I told Raymond -- this isn't\Njust about the person
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.83,0:19:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,that ordered\NElizabeth's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:14.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is also about that person\Nframing Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.58,0:19:15.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dembe's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.98,0:19:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever Heddie knows,\Nwhatever she's done --
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.55,0:19:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,she is Mr. Cooper's\Nbest chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to stay ahead\Nof Reddington.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.82,0:19:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Does anyone know\Nwhere Heddie is?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.36,0:19:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Miami.\NShe has a condo in Miami.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.43,0:19:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a helipad\Nin Islamorada.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.50,0:19:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll send a chopper.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.62,0:19:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You want that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.43,0:19:57.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.93,0:20:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,One more strawberry.\NYou want that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good puppy.\NYou want that one?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.54,0:20:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can hear right now\Nis Heddie's laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,All these years, that laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.89,0:20:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! No, no, no, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.56,0:20:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Heddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I guarantee it's unlocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.57,0:20:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Voil√†.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.48,0:20:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She was just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.66,0:20:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And then she was tipped off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.00,0:20:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I-I-I got out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be on the ground\Nin five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.27,0:20:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll pick you up around\Nthe corner at Flamingo Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.94,0:20:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.58,0:20:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true?\NIs what true?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.69,0:20:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't even know\Nwhat I'm being accused of.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.92,0:20:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have something to do\Nwith Keen's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.39,0:20:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.86,0:20:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How could you --\NIs that what you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what Raymond thinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I don't know\Nwhat's going on here,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.04,0:20:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,but I never did anything\Nto hurt Elizabeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.69,0:21:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.46,0:21:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dembe, come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.43,0:21:09.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Heddie, he's the one\Nyou'll have to convince.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.94,0:21:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Raymond.\NI know you have her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.68,0:21:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,We're just trying\Nto keep her safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.45,0:21:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what she might\Nhave been a part of?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.92,0:21:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What she could be\Nresponsible for?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.66,0:21:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Raymond, you're blinded\Nby anger right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.89,0:21:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd execute this woman\Nbefore you can get answers.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.07,0:21:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Harold is counting\Non those answers,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.84,0:21:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,so is the rest of the FBI,\Nand so are you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.11,0:21:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot kill Heddie\Nbefore you get the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.08,0:21:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I tell you what this\Nreminds me of.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.45,0:21:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The coast of\NMadagascar in 2010,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.92,0:21:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,on that stunning\NSpirit's Loop,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.03,0:21:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,all that beautiful mahogany\Nbright work.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.63,0:21:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it?\N80, 90 feet?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.91,0:21:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,111.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And then we saw the skiffs,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.05,0:21:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,pirates out of Nacala.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to fight.\NWe were certainly armed for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.56,0:21:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,High seas adventure.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.86,0:21:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But you insisted\Nwe stand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.93,0:21:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it you said to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.70,0:22:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrendering loses us\Nnothing we'll miss
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.74,0:22:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,but gives them\Nthe world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.11,0:22:04.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one shot was fired.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.98,0:22:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They took the boat,\Nthe brandy, my Sea-Dweller --
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.76,0:22:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I loved that watch.\NYou got another.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.03,0:22:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Spent six hours, us and the\Ncrew in that tiny life raft.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.77,0:22:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, Dembe, I've always respected\Nyour level-headedness,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.41,0:22:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,your refusal to just say yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.38,0:22:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,your willingness to put me\Nin my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.76,0:22:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I hardly see how what I said\Nthen applies to now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.03,0:22:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't either.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.16,0:22:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just killing time\Ntill we caught up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, Heddie, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.64,0:22:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.64,0:22:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.04,0:23:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Harold, take\Na look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.18,0:23:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Lacroix had a hell\Nof a movie collection, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.19,0:23:15.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I opened this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.16,0:23:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, there's\Nsome minor security here,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.20,0:23:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,just a password protection.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.00,0:23:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a minute to go ahead,\Nand here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.74,0:23:25.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's loading now.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.51,0:23:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.91,0:23:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a digitized record\Nof payment of some kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.85,0:23:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Lacroix and Reggie Cole\Nwere involved
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.69,0:23:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,in those\Ncivil settlement shakedowns.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.83,0:23:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Could this be that?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.83,0:23:36.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a lot of names here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.10,0:23:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That scam must've\Nbeen a lot bigger
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.57,0:23:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,than Lacroix and Cole.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.84,0:23:40.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's look for the names\Nwith the biggest numbers
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.54,0:23:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,next to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.94,0:23:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.78,0:23:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Lawrence Knoll\Nand Angela Sherwood.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.12,0:23:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Who were they?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.15,0:23:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Angela Sherwood for sure\Nand, yep, Knoll, too --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,they're both lawyers\Nat the same law firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.80,0:23:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's find out\Nwhat they know.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.24,0:23:58.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you two headed?\NWe got a lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.61,0:24:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe promising.\NWe don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.51,0:24:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I come\Nwith you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.75,0:24:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know\Nwhat you're walking into.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.19,0:24:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.09,0:24:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd be a violation\Nof bureau protocol.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.22,0:24:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And I have to pay attention\Nto that stuff now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.73,0:24:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Alina,\Nbut you're out of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.58,0:24:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.12,0:24:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Gramercy died in surgery two\Nhours ago of a gunshot wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.06,0:24:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Collateral damage\Nwas always a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.70,0:24:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,News is spreading\Nlike wildfire,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.57,0:24:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and his people knew\Nhe was meeting with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.87,0:24:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got half the criminal\Nunderworld asking me
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.24,0:24:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,if my boss murdered\Nthe head of Caelum Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.81,0:24:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.98,0:24:36.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I do.\NI just don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.59,0:24:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I have what I was after,\Nand I'm bringing her back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.59,0:24:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Her?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.70,0:24:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,It was Heddie, Marvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.73,0:24:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,All roads led to Heddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.20,0:24:48.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And so help me,\Nshe will atone for her sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.61,0:24:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm taking her to the warehouse\Nwhere I'm going to really
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.01,0:24:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,get to know\Nmy old friend, Heddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.75,0:24:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if that's the case,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.05,0:24:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be able to add\Nto your interrogation.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.32,0:24:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How so?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.93,0:24:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When you asked me to look\Ninto that bank account,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.26,0:25:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,that wasn't\Nthe only digging I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.27,0:25:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, I don't want to\Nspeak too soon --
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.04,0:25:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have to confirm\Nsomething first --
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.28,0:25:08.82,Default,,0,0,0,,but, uh, I may have\Na special guest
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.82,0:25:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,for you by the time\Nyou're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.92,0:25:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be there\Nin three hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.85,0:25:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,. We have your names here.\NWe have dollar amounts.Reginald Cole was bringing\Ncases to Tyson Lacroix
Dialogue: 0,0:25:28.79,0:25:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,who fraudulently settled\Nthose cases and kept the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.66,0:25:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If the two of you\Nweren't involved,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.07,0:25:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,then you knew about it.\NHow long do you thin --
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.17,0:25:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we stop you\Nright there?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.57,0:25:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,We know we're screwed.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.78,0:25:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We knew we were screwed\Nthe minute
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.84,0:25:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you showed up at the firm.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.11,0:25:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll deal.\NWe want statutory immunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.58,0:25:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll tell you\Nwhat we know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.79,0:25:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.26,0:25:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a sample.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.86,0:25:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We can give you names, more\Nnames than are in that document.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.00,0:25:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Lacroix might've kept records,\Nbut he wasn't Claudius.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.64,0:25:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't give you\NClaudius, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.24,0:25:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have\Nthat information.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.81,0:25:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Claudius?\NWho's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.71,0:25:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The mastermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.18,0:26:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The architect of the whole\Ndamn spider's web.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.89,0:26:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He dreamed\Nthe whole thing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.76,0:26:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Forcing settlements while\Nnever repping the clients
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.90,0:26:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,and pocketing\Nall the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.97,0:26:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It was genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.87,0:26:09.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Every one of us kicked back\Na percentage
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.87,0:26:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,of every\Ncase to Claudius.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.01,0:26:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There must have been a way\Nyou kept in touch with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.98,0:26:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything was done\Nthrough anonymous e-mails,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.89,0:26:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,burner phones -- real\Ncloak-and-dagger-type stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.89,0:26:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Personally, I never\Nbelieved there really was
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.90,0:26:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,a Claudius.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.97,0:26:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody somewhere would say\Nthey met him or her,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.20,0:26:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,but I never did.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.67,0:26:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Me neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.08,0:26:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said, we can\Ngive you other names.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.31,0:26:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't help you with the one\Nname you'd really want.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.22,0:26:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Raymond, I-I'm innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.06,0:26:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't understand what's\Ngoing on, but I'm telling you --
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.37,0:26:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, no, please,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.44,0:26:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard every variation\Non that theme before,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.71,0:26:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and I don't want\Nto hear it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.01,0:26:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No more bloviating.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.25,0:26:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.22,0:26:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It means I could wax poetic\Nabout the nature of betrayal
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.23,0:26:58.24,Default,,0,0,0,,or be begging your forgiveness\Nfor the rest of this flight,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.24,0:26:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.67,0:27:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Either way, I talk too much\Nand so do you.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.68,0:27:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.95,0:27:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So, please, do me a favor\Nand shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.30,0:27:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you done?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.97,0:27:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You know everything we're\Nlooking for depends
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.47,0:27:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,on the answers\NHeddie can provide,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.94,0:27:18.81,Default,,0,0,0,,not to mention you\Nalmost killed Dembe and Ressler.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.81,0:27:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I most certainly\Ndid not.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.21,0:27:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The airbags deployed,\Nand their egos were bruised.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.42,0:27:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't say that for\NHarris Gramercy, I found out.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.69,0:27:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That was poor luck,\Nbut it provided me
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.70,0:27:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,with one of the answers\NI'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.21,0:27:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you kill that woman,\Nwe'll lose everything valuable
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.98,0:27:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,she has to say about\Nthat's been going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.98,0:27:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,including how to find\Nthis mastermind Claudius.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.82,0:27:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never let her testify\Nin open court, Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.06,0:27:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:44.93,0:27:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.20,0:27:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hold my own trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.77,0:27:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll get\Nanswers for the both of us,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.17,0:27:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,you can count on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.34,0:27:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Agent Park, are you here to make\Na claim for Heddie, as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.48,0:27:58.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to ask a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.49,0:28:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a lot on my mind\Nthis evening,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.80,0:28:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but what can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.30,0:28:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.84,0:28:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I was thinking,\Nwith all that's going on --
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.17,0:28:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a job?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.48,0:28:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a job, just to stay\Na part of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.95,0:28:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're close\Nto Keen's killer --
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.89,0:28:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm good at what I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.22,0:28:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm, that's quite a bold line\Nfor me to cross.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.20,0:28:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I admit I made that leap before,\Nbut at the moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.94,0:28:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm swimming in hot water with\NHarold and the FBI as it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.21,0:28:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The FBI doesn't\Nwant me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.95,0:28:29.92,Default,,0,0,0,,They've made that clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.46,0:28:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Alina, I can see\Nyou're suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.03,0:28:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And with your maladies\Nas they are...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.20,0:28:39.87,Default,,0,0,0,,...there's no task
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.87,0:28:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I can afford or even feel\Nright about offering you.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.21,0:28:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, I've had about all\NI can stand of people telling me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.85,0:28:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,what I can and can't do.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.99,0:28:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I've made enough\Nmistakes for one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.93,0:28:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making another one\Nright now.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.50,0:28:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help you today,\NAgent Park.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.54,0:29:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to attend\Nto another matter at hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.30,0:29:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.25,0:29:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.48,0:29:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can\Ntake care of myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.16,0:29:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Raymond,\NHeddie is waking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.10,0:29:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll talk tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.88,0:29:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You should exit\Nout the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.57,0:29:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.44,0:29:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Not one stone has been unturned.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.11,0:29:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The lawyers were a dead end.\NReddington had Heddie.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.95,0:29:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.99,0:29:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I appreciate your faith,\Nbut what else is there to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.26,0:30:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We do it all again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.90,0:30:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,All of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.34,0:30:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Park found that payout record\Non a disc somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.11,0:30:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,where it wasn't\Nsupposed to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.34,0:30:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What else is here\Nthat we might've missed?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.45,0:30:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't miss anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:10.85,0:30:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to bet\Nyour life on that?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.29,0:30:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Or do you want to help me\Nlook again?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.20,0:30:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,.\NDidn't expect\Nanyone to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:34.37,0:30:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I guess I just love\Nmy job --
Dialogue: 0,0:30:36.37,0:30:38.37,Default,,0,0,0,,double-checking\NTyson Lacroix's entire
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.38,0:30:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,John Grisham\Nmovie collection.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.35,0:30:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been gone a while.\NYou okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.49,0:30:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to Reddington\Nand offered him my help.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.49,0:30:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.\NHe rejected me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.53,0:30:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a place\Nthere, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:51.40,0:30:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not, because\Nyour place is here next to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.38,0:30:57.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I know desk work doesn't have\Nthe thrill of the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.45,0:31:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,but what we do in here,\Nit saves lives, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.32,0:31:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Help save mine. Right now,\NI could really use you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.06,0:31:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.37,0:31:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the other half\Nof this pile.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.97,0:31:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I'm going cross-eyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.52,0:31:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Marvin will be back\Nin a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.22,0:31:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is the time to speak freely.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:19.22,0:31:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You think that I had\Nsomething to do
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.23,0:31:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,with Elizabeth's death?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.64,0:31:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But why?\NWhat reason would I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.44,0:31:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,History's full of unlikely\Ncharacters and unlikely events.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.02,0:31:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.42,0:31:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The coordination alone,\Nforget about the planning,
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.29,0:31:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and you never found out?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.66,0:31:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That's something\Nyou actually believe?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.00,0:31:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You either had help\Nor you helped someone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.24,0:31:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, helped who?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.48,0:31:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Or helped from who?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.11,0:31:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,From where?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.52,0:31:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do I look anything other\Nthan hopelessly alone right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.56,0:31:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Raymond,\Nthis is Micky Croft.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.40,0:31:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Micky is the arms trade\Nalong the Canadian border.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.47,0:32:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I know who he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.04,0:32:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your reputation precedes you\Nas reasonable and reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.58,0:32:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Likewise.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.38,0:32:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I was looking for any of\Nour people
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.09,0:32:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,who might've been disloyal,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.59,0:32:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,maybe shopped\Naround their services,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.13,0:32:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and that's when I found Micky,\Nheard his story.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.63,0:32:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,She came to me --\Nhas to be three years ago now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.64,0:32:19.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Said she was looking\Nfor employment opportunities,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.65,0:32:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,said she was done\Nwith how you ran things.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.55,0:32:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,She showed me how you\Ncook your books.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.73,0:32:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,She's a real whiz\Nwith dodging tax law.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.10,0:32:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she is.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.37,0:32:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I only listened 'cause\NI thought she was
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.10,0:32:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,all the way\Ngone from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.34,0:32:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Heddie?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:37.61,0:32:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you\Nwant me to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.49,0:32:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You never thought\NI was anything special.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.13,0:32:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I was overlooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.33,0:32:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So I went\Nhunting for work.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.61,0:32:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I be killed\Nfor wanting a better job?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.75,0:32:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Micky, I appreciate\Nyou coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.22,0:32:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.69,0:33:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if you wouldn't mind\Nfinding your way back out
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.59,0:33:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to the comfort\Nof Marvin's car.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.60,0:33:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Micky.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:16.16,0:33:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get on with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.36,0:33:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's late.\NSun will be up soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.32,0:33:32.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Make it quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.67,0:33:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.74,0:33:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.38,0:33:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now we have to deal\Nwith the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.48,0:34:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that I killed\NHarris Gramercy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.48,0:34:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,His clients will be out\Nfor blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.39,0:34:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to deal\Nwith that this minute?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.16,0:34:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll fly to Latvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.69,0:34:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Several of his biggest clients\Nare based thereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.60,0:34:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can call a meeting,\Nperhaps we can plead our case.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.71,0:34:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Jet's waiting\Non the runway.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.49,0:34:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Marvin, you coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.80,0:34:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hon.\NI know it's late.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.77,0:34:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be here a while.\NThey need me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.44,0:34:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm watching a wedding video\Nof two people that are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.82,0:34:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.26,0:34:42.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll text you when --
Dialogue: 0,0:34:42.86,0:34:45.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hon, I got to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.17,0:34:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the videos\Nwas the Lacroix wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.37,0:34:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly as it was labeled,\Nright?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.34,0:34:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing to see there.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.68,0:34:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Except I watched it anyway.\NYou were right.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.49,0:34:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a thrill,\Nbut damn it if desk work
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.52,0:34:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,isn't gonna save your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.26,0:34:59.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, that's enough\Nembarrassing stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.30,0:35:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,And now for someone who's\Nvery special
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.43,0:35:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to both\NTyson and Michelle,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.84,0:35:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,a lifelong friend\Nand Tyson's best man.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.75,0:35:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,To Michelle and Tyson,\NI love you guys so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.69,0:35:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,May I only find my own\NMichelle one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.63,0:35:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,To Michelle and Tyson.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.67,0:35:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,May their marriage\Nbe blessed forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.28,0:35:23.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.59,0:35:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's00 a.m.\Nin Latvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.92,0:35:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We have 10 hours\Nof flying time --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.66,0:35:34.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold that thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.57,0:35:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Harold.\NWhere are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.30,0:35:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.44,0:35:38.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Red eye to Riga.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.91,0:35:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Marvin's here, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.71,0:35:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Reddington,\Nlisten to me carefully --
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.38,0:35:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,you cannot trust\NMarvin Gerard.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.52,0:35:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Come again?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.79,0:35:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tyson Lacroix\Nand Marvin Gerard
Dialogue: 0,0:35:47.83,0:35:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,were old friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.93,0:35:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,They've known each other\Nfor decades.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.67,0:35:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Reddington, I can't connect\Nall the dots,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.84,0:35:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,but something is very wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.30,0:35:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Harold, I appreciate\Nthe call.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.75,0:35:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What's Edward doing?\NAre we gonna take off soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.89,0:36:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably flipping\Nswitches, checking gauges,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.39,0:36:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,plotting our course.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.28,0:36:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What -- What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.56,0:36:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this? I don't --\NI don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.56,0:36:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure Heddie is\Nas interested as I am
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.27,0:36:29.61,Default,,0,0,0,,to hear how and why\Nyou did what you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.61,0:36:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm gonna\Nhave a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.62,0:36:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pour.\NHm.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.32,0:36:40.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And I hope your story is good.\NYour life depends on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.79,0:36:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.00,0:36:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I am the most loyal\Nto you and always have been.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.97,0:37:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But I never swore an oath\Nto Elizabeth Keen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.84,0:37:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I never made it a secret\Nthat I didn't trust her.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.75,0:37:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,She was unworthy\Nand unqualified.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.02,0:37:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,To have her run things?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.63,0:37:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Over my dead body.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.36,0:37:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Careful what you\Nwish for, Marvin.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.88,0:37:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything I did,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.75,0:37:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I did in the best interest\Nof your empire.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.89,0:37:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,After Elizabeth's death,\Nwhen you took off,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.39,0:37:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I kept things going\Nas best I could,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.53,0:37:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,and I did\Na pretty damn good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.90,0:37:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When you came back, I --
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.47,0:37:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd finally\Nbe over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.91,0:37:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You've lived your life\Nwith so much death and loss.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.79,0:37:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You've always\Ngotten over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.89,0:37:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But you were\Nutterly determined
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.93,0:37:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to get to the bottom\Nof how she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.67,0:37:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And I couldn't\Nlet that happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.64,0:37:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried everything I could\Nto slow you down, to stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.65,0:37:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I went after your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.38,0:37:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I had my own\Nfriends killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.99,0:38:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I went after Harold.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.40,0:38:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.40,0:38:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You just kept coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.67,0:38:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So then you went after me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.71,0:38:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Serving you up, Heddie,\Nwas a last resort
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.42,0:38:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,to protect my life\Nwith Raymond.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.09,0:38:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I am anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.06,0:38:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my life --\NRaymond Reddington.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.84,0:38:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What a waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.41,0:38:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What a terrible,\Nterrible waste.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.89,0:38:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you\Nfigure it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.56,0:38:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.83,0:38:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gone over it\Nand over it,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.60,0:38:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,thought of it\Nand thought of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.87,0:38:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember the day\NElizabeth died
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.71,0:38:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,better than entire years\Nof my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.45,0:38:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember what she wore,\Nthe smell of rain in the air.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.86,0:38:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The sound of her voice.\NThe last words she spoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.00,0:38:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The look in her eyes\Nin that moment,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.97,0:39:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,that last moment\Nwhen she looked at me,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.45,0:39:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,as if for the first time\Nseeing me for who I really was.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.60,0:39:12.14,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd forgotten\Nabout the headache
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.14,0:39:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,until today when Agent Park\Nwas in front of me
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.01,0:39:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,with her headache\Nand a glass shattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.12,0:39:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,All the time I spent agonizing\Nover that GPS tracker
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.16,0:39:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that Elizabeth ingested,\Nwhere it came from.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.11,0:39:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'd forgotten\Nabout Elizabeth's headache.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.08,0:39:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The morning of her death,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.02,0:39:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,we stopped by your office\Nto sign some paperwork,
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.16,0:39:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,transfer some holdings.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.50,0:39:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We had tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.51,0:39:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She had coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.04,0:39:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What was in it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.08,0:39:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,She got a headache,\Nand you gave her aspirin.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.06,0:40:01.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how you bugged her.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.51,0:40:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You did it\Nright in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:09.05,0:40:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why this ruse with Heddie\Nat the warehouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.79,0:40:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,the -- the gunshot.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.56,0:40:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can answer that.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.03,0:40:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Raymond wanted to make you\Nfeel safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.64,0:40:22.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Feel safe for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.81,0:40:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,To get you on the plane.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.85,0:40:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be a nice, long flight,\Ngive us time to clear
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.69,0:40:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,your offices and apartment,\Nthe place at the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.76,0:40:34.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough time to sift\Nthrough everything
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.83,0:40:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and decide\Nwhat to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.68,0:40:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you need\Nto get that?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.69,0:40:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.00,0:40:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:50.73,0:40:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,When I drove\Nto the warehouse,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.61,0:40:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know\Nif I was in the clear yet
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.11,0:41:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so I put a small\Ninsurance plan in place...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.25,0:41:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.01,0:41:16.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I sent a panic alert with this\Nwatch five minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.18,0:41:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If my shooter doesn't hear\Nfrom me in the next two minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.79,0:41:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,he'll splatter her lovely mind\Nall over that trailer.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.04,0:41:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm walking\Noff this plane,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:32.68,0:41:36.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and you are\Ngoing to let me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.89,0:41:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!\NWeecha!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.63,0:41:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Weecha!\NYou'll kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.27,0:41:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:46.61,0:41:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I never\Nwanted any of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.63,0:41:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You've had an odd way\Nof showing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.30,0:42:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You -- You're the one\Nwho showed me the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.84,0:42:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Those recordings you left\Nfor Elizabeth
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.18,0:42:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,telling her how\Nto run things --
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.32,0:42:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran them\Nwhile you were gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.76,0:42:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I've run them\Nsince you've been back.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.04,0:42:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,May the best man win,\Nold friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.78,0:42:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, Claudius.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.65,0:42:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Raymond, help!\NPlease!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.65,0:42:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Weecha, Weecha, Weecha.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:28.06,0:42:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Weecha, Weecha?
